{"tid":759278,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔憂愁、傷心· 身體語言","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T12:43:06.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba05aab75a9fc8d2dc5e17d62f4bbbd9f3be9d9","tid":759278,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了。以下video 可看到牠憂愁：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0beosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=49b5b911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。（我會有個post 關於垂耳兔和非垂耳兔子驚慌的身體語言）<br />\n<br />\n日本很有名的兔仔島：大久野島 - 島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay等等。給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0beosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=75693726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更多關於兔子憂愁的身體語言：</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0beosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3f08fc41\" target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a>"}]}